Open close principle say that Software Component should be closed for modification but open for extensions

Closed for modification : 

New feature added to software component donot have to modify existing code, 

Software component should be extendible to add a new feature or to add a new behavior to it 

following open close principle benefits us in having considerable cose savings 

we also saw that how open closed principle and Single responsibility principle can work together to have a better design 

Also we cautioned , we can create huge number of unnecceary claases , by simply blindly following open close principle 
with out applying  any thought 
